    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Compilations of separate articles, treatises, studies, or literary compositions of various kinds brought together into one volume. For compilations of brief extracts of works that are considered the best examples of an author, subject matter, or literary form, use "anthologies."</Note_Text>
